Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------NEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也在第二天完全好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起游泳游到傍晚  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回来的时候  大家都没换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,句号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下叫我们来帮忙准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是联接着九个世界的世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其本质被认为是世界本身的体现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  我们能像这样在这里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全是靠着世界树支撑着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  一年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借着感谢世界树的机会大家一起热闹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个祭典  公主殿下要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  守护这块土地的梦魔的王族有作为代表唱歌  跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来表达对世界树的感谢的传统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  从上一代开始方向就偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下  去年没有能参加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是宣布今年要自己来唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表达对世界树的感谢是祭典的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说殿下想表达对世界树的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后问题就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年没能参加的殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能改变其心情的事  到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示和世界树有关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  果然还是作为的王族的自觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下想对能与直哉大人相遇的世界树表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  像我这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉大人的谦虚虽然也是美德  但也要分场合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够与直哉大人相遇真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连殿下的真心也想否定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该  该去给大家帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一半是瞎猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  有点那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太生硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  琉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂唱歌跳舞本来是很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要在大家面前不紧张  像平常一样发挥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么就只有特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  一起来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉内裤  制造胆量的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  茶准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（调教中）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  回来的好…快？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（调教  完毕）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂  变得很熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来正式的时候也没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还差的远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂大人  请加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会一起跳舞支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起洗么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室很大没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次和朋友一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的露天浴池可是被记入妖魔界百景之一  非常有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都能进这样的浴室  好羡慕啊  露蒂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉卡的衣服很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在故乡的话是不会穿这种衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连内裤也是  来到这国家之后才第一次穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  不穿的话感觉很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我也是  穿运动短裤的时候也不穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接穿的么  真是有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天我也第一次体验了  奇妙的紧张感让人觉得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜丝特那个大概不算太健康吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14岁就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（受打击）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:10:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种成长是有个人差别的  还是不要太在意比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}梦魔是很早熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说母亲也是在我这个年龄就已经很波涛汹涌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}不  不过  并不是越大越好吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸好像喜欢大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  我的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然刚洗完澡就是要喝牛奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我那个国家的固定桥段哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我也习惯在洗完澡之后喝乳牛魔族乳母的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳牛魔族的鲜奶里含有能促进女性身体发育的特殊营养
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也一直有喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要在洗完澡之后啊殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在洗澡促进血液循环之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向胸部输送营养的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替换的衣服拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么慢真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（艾尔芙的牛奶是最高级的极品）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔芙  请给我牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想胸部变大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很清楚  不过好像很欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想再变大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经够大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下她们好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能变大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  很完美的  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果是冰的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要继续加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你已经够大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大家请快点换衣服  会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂  大家在等你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  都已经练习那么多时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  这种气氛真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉兴奋起来了  大家都穿着浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人间界一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是从东方的国度传来的东西  轻便凉爽真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说等会儿再过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话  话说回来  明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:14:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说虽然有点奇怪  这样真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  浴衣的时候是不穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不只是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的浴衣和其它人穿的很不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今年的流行款式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会和艾莉卡在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才偶然遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打扰到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣很合身啊  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把内裤脱了  否则不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶说过穿浴衣时不穿内裤是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  明日叶  你又说了些多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大家  尽情地去享受祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶你真…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  不好意思在兴头上打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的那个很那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  露蒂酱  你的浴衣装也真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  我们正要开始玩呢  你不要来烦我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟  你们不要误会我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的身体也痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再一次申请和你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（THE  复仇）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉这人那么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们决一胜负来证明谁更适合露蒂酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  我的爸爸才不可能会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  直哉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话就必须接受他的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干翻他  直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能给那孩子丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这么定了  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子  你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的宿敌  但是胜负从现在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经走了  王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  竟然逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混账
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混账
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时  时间要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  已经这个时候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会在这里看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家看看你特训的成果  露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下  你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  直哉带着的明日叶备用内裤已经穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  再怎么样也不能让公主殿下那个样子上台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才呢  看到店里有卖就买下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这样就和我的是一对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚斯塔露蒂殿下  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉  明日叶
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------IN------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:44.90,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是粉色的草莓蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:54.09,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是桃色的草莓雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:20:00.03,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摆不定的心闪耀着  你看  重合在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:05.92,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指和手指缠在一起  来吧  握住彼此的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:12.69,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散播到全世界去  比风儿还快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:18.95,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那幸福的旋律  粉红的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:25.01,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于终于连在了一起  嘴边传来甜美之味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:27.07,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软绵绵的一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:32.41,in1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的桃色心
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------IN------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（亲）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我要把今天的事都记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写好了  锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到这里快乐的事多得都写不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  暑假马上就要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假结束后该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\bord4}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作业啊  我也做过植物图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为是颗豌豆去摘  谁知道是只蚱蜢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道明日叶和公主殿下会不会一直记得这个夏天所发生的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:43.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(489,288)}两人独处的句号
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------OP------------------
